NK041(di)002:1: // a mri ta ni d+hi ku m+b+ha a sh+ta ma ng+ga lam s+ya p+au dza n+aa ma ti sma ///
NK041(di)002:2: bkra shis brgyad pa'i mchod chog bdud rtsi'i gter bum zhes bya ba bzhugs /
NK041(di)002:4: las gang zhig rtsom pa'i thog mar dkon mchog gi
NK041(di)002:5: rten gyi spyan sngar ci 'byor ba'i mchod pa bshams
NK041(di)002:6: la / skyabs sems sngon du 'gro bas /
NK041(di)002:7: mchog gsum tshogs gnyis chos dbyings bden stobs kyis //
NK041(di)002:8: snod bcud dag pa'i zhing gi 'byor pa'i dbus //
NK041(di)002:9: rin chen gzhal med bkod mdzes gdan khri dang //
NK041(di)002:10: phul byung mchod pa'i sprin gyis mdzes gyur cig /
NK041(di)002:11: mchod pa'i sprin gzung dang rten snying bzla /
NK041(di)002:12: mtshan tsam thos pas bkra shis dpal 'phel ba'i //
NK041(di)002:13: rgyal dang de sras sems dpa' sems ma'i tshogs //
NK041(di)002:14: 'jig rten skyong ba sde dang bcas pa rnams //
NK041(di)002:15: thugs rje thugs dam dbang gis 'dir gshegs shing //
NK041(di)002:16: gtsang sbyar mchod yon dag byed khrus kyi chab //
NK041(di)002:17: rnam bkra'i rgyan chas yid 'ong gdan khrir bcas //
NK041(di)002:18: gus pas 'bul lo ci bder bzhes nas kyang //
NK041(di)002:19: brtan par bzhugs la bkra shis 'phel bar mdzod //
NK041(di)002:20: zhes spyan drangs nas mdun rten dang tha mi dad du bzhugs par mos la //
NK041(di)002:21: snang srid rnam dag chos dbyings gzhal yas su //
NK041(di)002:22: rang byung ye shes 'jam dpal gzhon nu'i sku //
NK041(di)002:23: yid 'ong nyi ma 'char ka'i lang tsho can //
NK041(di)002:24: dang po'i phyag gnyis ral gri ut+pa la //
NK041(di)002:25: tha ma'i phyag gnyis nor bu bum bzang bsnams //
NK041(di)002:26: dar dang rin chen rgyan rdzogs skyil krung gis //
NK041(di)002:27: rab mdzes pad+ma zla ba'i gdan steng na //
NK041(di)002:28: dpag bsam shing la sku rgyab brten nas bzhugs //
NK041(di)002:29: bkra shis lha mo brgyad la sogs pa yis //
NK041(di)002:30: rab 'byams mchod pa'i sprin gyis mkha' dbyings 'gengs //
NK041(di)002:31: dran pa tsam gyis phun tshogs dpal yon kun //
NK041(di)002:32: yid bzhin legs par stsol ba'i bdag nyid la //
NK041(di)002:33: ma lus phyogs dus zhing gi rgyal ba dang //
NK041(di)002:34: rgyal ba sras bcas til gang ltar bzhugs pas //
NK041(di)002:35: me tog char 'bebs shis pa'i glu dbyangs sgrogs //
NK041(di)002:36: ye shes 'od zer 'bar bas mkha' khyab gsal //
NK041(di)002:38: de nas phyag mchod sogs 'bul ba ni //
NK041(di)002:39: snang srid rnam dag rang bzhin lhun grub pa'i //
NK041(di)002:40: bkra shis phyogs bcu'i zhing na bzhugs pa yi //
NK041(di)002:41: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun 'phags pa'i tshogs //
NK041(di)002:42: kun la phyag 'tshal mchod 'bul skyabs su mchi //
NK041(di)002:43: sgron me'i rgyal po rtsal brtan don grub dgongs //
NK041(di)002:44: byams pa'i rgyan dpal dge grags dpal dam pa //
NK041(di)002:45: kun la dgongs pa rgya cher grags pa can //
NK041(di)002:46: lhun po ltar 'phags rtsal grags dpal dang ni //
NK041(di)002:47: sems can thams cad la dgongs grags pa'i dpal //
NK041(di)002:48: yid tshim mdzad pa rtsal rab grags dpal te //
NK041(di)002:49: mtshan tsam thos pa'i bkra shis dpal 'phel ba //
NK041(di)002:50: bde bar gshegs pa brgyad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK041(di)002:51: 'jam dpal gzhon nu dpal ldan rdo rje 'dzin //
NK041(di)002:52: spyan ras gzigs dbang mgon po byams pa'i dpal //
NK041(di)002:53: sa yi snying po sgrib pa rnam par sel //
NK041(di)002:54: nam mkha'i snying po 'phags mchog kun tu bzang //
NK041(di)002:55: ut+pala rdo rje pad dkar klu shing dang //
NK041(di)002:56: nor bu zla ba ral gri nyi ma yi //
NK041(di)002:57: phyag mtshan legs bsnams bkra shis dpal gyi mchog /
NK041(di)002:58: byang chub sems dpa' brgyad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK041(di)002:59: rin chen gdugs mchog bkra shis gser gyi nya //
NK041(di)002:60: 'dod 'byung bum bzang yid 'ong ka ma la //
NK041(di)002:61: snyan grags dung dang phun tshogs dpal be'u //
NK041(di)002:62: mi nub rgyal mtshan dbang bsgyur 'khor lo ste //
NK041(di)002:63: rin chen rtags mchog brgyad kyi phyag mtshan can //
NK041(di)002:64: phyogs dus rgyal ba mchod cing dgyes bskyed ma //
NK041(di)002:65: sgeg sogs ngo bo dran pas dpal spel ba'i //
NK041(di)002:66: bkra shis lha mo brgyad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK041(di)002:67: tshangs pa chen po bde 'byung sred med bu //
NK041(di)002:68: mig stong ldan dang rgyal po yul 'khor srung //
NK041(di)002:69: 'phags skyes po dang klu dbang mig mi bzang //
NK041(di)002:70: rnam thos sras te lha rdzas 'khor lo dang //
NK041(di)002:71: tri shu la dang mdung thung rdo rje can //
NK041(di)002:72: pi wam ral gri mchod rten rgyal mtshan 'dzin //
NK041(di)002:73: sa gsum gnas su dge legs bkra shis spel //
NK041(di)002:74: 'jig rten skyong ba brgyad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK041(di)002:75: dngos su bshams dang yid kyis rnam sprul pa'i //
NK041(di)002:76: dri med yid 'ong lha rdzas bkod pa'i char //
NK041(di)002:77: me tog bdug spos snang gsal dri yi mchog /
NK041(di)002:78: zhal zas rol mo rnam lnga'i 'dod yon rdzas //
NK041(di)002:79: bkra shis rtag rdzas rgyal srid rin chen bdun //
NK041(di)002:80: nye ba'i rin chen bdun dang glu gar ma //
NK041(di)002:81: mdzes sdug bkod pa'i rol mo mtha' yas pa //
NK041(di)002:82: 'bul lo bzhes nas bkra shis 'phel bar mdzod //
NK041(di)002:83: bdag gzhan thogs med dus nas da lta'i bar //
NK041(di)002:84: mi shes nyon mongs sgrib pa'i tshogs kun bshags //
NK041(di)002:85: bsod nams kun la dga' bas yi rangs shing //
NK041(di)002:86: chos 'khor bskor bzhin rtag par bzhugs gsol 'debs //
NK041(di)002:87: 'dis mtshon dus gsum bsags pa'i dge tshogs rnams //
NK041(di)002:88: byang chub chen por yongs su bsngo byed cing //
NK041(di)002:89: rgyal ba sras bcas dgyes pa'i brtul zhugs mchog /
NK041(di)002:90: srog gi phyir yang mi gtong bzung bar bgyi //
NK041(di)002:91: mgon po ye shes sgrib pa mi mnga' bas //
NK041(di)002:92: bdag gi lhag pa'i bsam pa khyed kyis mkhyen //
NK041(di)002:93: thugs dam ma bsnyel dgongs pa'i rtsal bskyed la //
NK041(di)002:94: ji ltar gsol btab 'bras bu mchis par mdzod //
NK041(di)002:95: bdag cag deng 'dir bya ba rtsom pa la //
NK041(di)002:96: gegs dang nye bar 'tshe ba kun zhi nas //
NK041(di)002:97: 'dod don dpal 'phel bsam don yid bzhin 'grub //
NK041(di)002:98: bkra shis bde legs phun sum tshogs par shog /
NK041(di)002:99: ces lan gsum sogs ci rigs dang /
NK041(di)002:101: rang byung thugs rje'i bdag nyid bcom ldan 'das //
NK041(di)002:102: mkhyen brtse nus pa mtshungs med rdo rje'i sku //
NK041(di)002:103: ma lus 'gro ba'i gtan gyi mgon gyur pa //
NK041(di)002:104: skyabs mchog dam pa bdag la dgongs su gsol //
NK041(di)002:105: khyod ni rang byung ye shes bde ba che //
NK041(di)002:106: ma lus 'gro kun khyod kyi ngang gyur kyang //
NK041(di)002:107: mi shis rgud pas mnar ba bdag cag la //
NK041(di)002:108: deng nas rtag pa dam pa'i mchog stsol cig /
NK041(di)002:109: bkra shis kun gyi bkra shis bla med pa //
NK041(di)002:110: grags pa'i bkra shis snyan grags dge mtshan ldan //
NK041(di)002:111: dbugs 'byin chen po dga' ston rgya che ba //
NK041(di)002:112: dga' chen rol mo chen pos dbugs dbung stsol //
NK041(di)002:113: 'jam dpal dpal dang ldan pa'i mchog gyur pa //
NK041(di)002:114: mchod sbyin rdo rjes bdag la ma chog stsol cig /
NK041(di)002:115: de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi ye shes sku'i //
NK041(di)002:116: ye shes rdo rje'i dbang bskur bdag la stsol //
NK041(di)002:117: 'dod 'byung de bzhin nor bu chen po 'chang //
NK041(di)002:118: dpag bsam shing chen rgyas pa 'gro kun gsos //
NK041(di)002:119: khyab bdag rin chen kun mchog dbul ba sel //
NK041(di)002:120: bum bzang che mchog bdag la dpal gyur cig /
NK041(di)002:121: dengs nas bla med byang chub ma thob pa'i //
NK041(di)002:122: tshe rabs kun tu khyod kyis rjes bzung ste //
NK041(di)002:123: mi mthun rgud pa thams cad rgyun chad nas //
NK041(di)002:124: dpal dang skal bzang bkra shis bde legs mdzod //
NK041(di)002:127: nyin par bkra shis bgegs zhi bsam don 'grub //
NK041(di)002:128: mtshan mor bkra shis rmi lam bzang dgu mthong //
NK041(di)002:129: dus kun bkra shis snyan grags rlung rta spel //
NK041(di)002:130: rnam kun bkra shis bde legs 'phel bar mdzod //
NK041(di)002:131: lha yi bkra shis ngo mtshar 'brug sgra sgrogs //
NK041(di)002:132: klu yi bkra shis dpal 'byor mtsho ltar bskyil //
NK041(di)002:133: mi yi bkra shis dkar chos rnam par 'phel //
NK041(di)002:134: kun kyang bkra shis chos srid brtan par mdzod //
NK041(di)002:135: bla ma'i bkra shis byin rlabs sprin phung 'khrigs //
NK041(di)002:136: yi dam bkra shis grub gnyis char du bsnyil //
NK041(di)002:137: mkha' 'gro'i bkra shis 'phrin las rtsi sman rgyas //
NK041(di)002:138: rtsa gsum bkra shis don gnyis lhun grub mdzod //
NK041(di)002:139: sangs rgyas bkra shis spangs rtogs bcud kyis gtam //
NK041(di)002:140: dam chos bkra shis bden gnyis 'dod pa 'jo //
NK041(di)002:141: dge 'dun bkra shis nyes pa'i gdung kun sel //
NK041(di)002:142: mchog gsum bkra shis srid na brtan par mdzod //
NK041(di)002:143: chos sku'i bkra shis zag med gter gyi 'byor //
NK041(di)002:144: longs sku'i bkra shis rtag brtan lhun gyis grub //
NK041(di)002:145: sprul sku'i bkra 'dul bzhi'i phrin las rgyas //
NK041(di)002:146: sku gsum bkra shis 'bad med lhun grub mdzod //
NK041(di)002:147: so thar bkra shis nges 'byung zhing sa gshin //
NK041(di)002:148: byang sems bkra shis gzhan phan myu gu rgyas //
NK041(di)002:149: gsang sngags bkra shis rim gnyis 'bras bus phyug /
NK041(di)002:150: sdom gsum bkra shis bslab gas gong 'phel mdzod //
NK041(di)002:151: thog mar bkra shis gzhi rgyud bee d+aur+ya //
NK041(di)002:152: gsang sngags bkra shis rim gnyis 'bras bus phyug /
NK041(di)002:153: sdom gsum bkra shis bslab gas gong 'phel mdzod //
NK041(di)002:154: thog mar bkra shis gzhi rgyud bee d+aur+ya //
NK041(di)002:155: bar du bkra shis lam rgyud byi dor mkhas //
NK041(di)002:156: tha mar bkra shis 'bras rgyud 'dod pa 'jo //
NK041(di)002:157: dus gsum bkra shis rtag brtan lhun grub mdzod //
NK041(di)002:158: bla ma'i bkra shis smin grol gdams zab 'jo //
NK041(di)002:159: slob ma'i bkra shis dad dam rnam par dag /
NK041(di)002:160: bla slob bkra shis bshad sgrub phyogs su 'grigs //
NK041(di)002:161: rgyal bstan bkra shis srid mthar 'phel rgyas mdzod //
NK041(di)002:162: snod kyi bkra shis dge bcu g.yang du 'khyil //
NK041(di)002:163: bcud kyi bkra shis tshe dpal 'byor tshogs rgyas //
NK041(di)002:164: snod bcud bkra shis rten 'byung gcig tu tshogs //
NK041(di)002:165: thar grol bkra shis 'bras bus 'byor par mdzod //
NK041(di)002:166: mchod gnas bkra shis bsdu bzhi'i phrin las rgyas //
NK041(di)002:167: yon bdag bkra shis sde bzhi'i mnga' thang dar //
NK041(di)002:168: mchod yon bkra shis rnam dkar 'bras bus phyug /
NK041(di)002:169: kun kyang bkra shis bde legs 'phel rgyas mdzod //
NK041(di)002:170: ces 'dod pa'i don la gsol ba gdab //
NK041(di)002:172: bkra shis pa'i gso sbyong dang /
NK041(di)002:175: lha dang klu dang gnod sbyin mi rnams dang //
NK041(di)002:176: phyogs bcu'i byang chub sems dpa'i mchod pa rnams //
NK041(di)002:177: yon tan chen po 'jig rten gtso la 'bul //
NK041(di)002:178: mchog gi mchod pa dam pa bzhes su gsol //
NK041(di)002:180: bkra shis kun gyi bkra shis dpal gyur ba //
NK041(di)002:181: grags pa'i bkra shis snyan grags chen po dge //
NK041(di)002:182: dbugs 'byin chen po rgyal ba sras bcas la //
NK041(di)002:183: gus pas bstod do 'dod dgu'i dngos grub rtsol //
NK041(di)002:184: rtag par dge ba'i bshes kyi rjes bzung zhing //
NK041(di)002:185: tshul gnas thos bsam bsgom pa'i yon tan rdzogs //
NK041(di)002:186: rmad byung byang chub sems kyi rten 'brel gyis //
NK041(di)002:187: bstan 'gro'i don chen 'grub par mdzad du gsol //
NK041(di)002:188: bde gshegs sras bcas kun gyi thugs bskyed dang //
NK041(di)002:189: mdzad pa smon lam mkhyen brtse nus pa'i tshul //
NK041(di)002:190: bla med ye shes sgyu 'phrul ji 'dra bar //
NK041(di)002:191: de 'dra kho nar bdag sogs 'gyur bar shog /
NK041(di)002:192: khyed la dad cing gsol ba btab pa'i mthus //
NK041(di)002:193: bdag sogs gang du gnas pa'i sa phyogs der //
NK041(di)002:194: nad gdon dbul 'phongs 'thab rtsod zhi ba dang //
NK041(di)002:195: chos dang bkra shis 'phel bar mdzad du gsol //
NK041(di)002:196: phan bde'i 'byung gnas bstan pa 'phel gyur cig /
NK041(di)002:197: tshe rabs kun tu chos la spyod gyur cig /
NK041(di)002:198: rgyal khams kun tu bkra shis rgyas gyur cig /
NK041(di)002:199: 'gro kun phyams shig sangs rgyas thob par shog /
NK041(di)002:200: ci ltar rigs pa'i 'dod don gsol zhing /
NK041(di)002:201: spro na mdun gyi tshogs rten rnams kyis shis brjod kyi me tog gtor bar mos la /
NK041(di)002:202: 'jam mgon bla ma'i gsung bkra shis mchog grub kyang bklag cing me tog gi char bsnying bar bya'o //
NK041(di)002:203: rjes nongs pa bzod gsol sogs spyi ltar bya'o //
NK041(di)002:204: de ltar bgyis pa'i phan yon yang //
NK041(di)002:205: ldang tshe brjod na de nyid don kun 'grub //
NK041(di)002:206: nyal tshe brjod na rmi lam bzang po mthong //
NK041(di)002:207: g.yul du 'jug tshe brjod na phyogs las rgyal //
NK041(di)002:208: bya ba rtsom dus brjod na 'dod don 'phel //
NK041(di)002:209: rgyun du brjod na tshe dpal grags 'byor shis //
NK041(di)002:210: bde legs phun tshogs bsam don yid bzhin 'grub //
NK041(di)002:211: sdig sgrib kun byang mngon mtho nges legs kyi //
NK041(di)002:212: don kun 'grub pa rgyal ba mchog gis gsungs //
NK041(di)002:213: zhes pa'i tshul la spro ba bskyed de rtag tu brtson par bya'o //
NK041(di)002:214: zhes pa'ang bya bral ba 'jam dbyangs blo gros rgya
NK041(di)002:215: mtsho'i sgra dbyangs kyis kun mkhyen bla ma 'jam dpal
NK041(di)002:216: dgyes pa'i rdo rje'i gsung las btus te brgyad bde
NK041(di)002:217: gshegs 'dus pa'i tshogs khang rang byung brag gi ke'u
